      "title": "Sri Lanka stocks down over 1-pct in mid-day trade",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 SriLanka stocks slip over 1% in mid-day trade on July 06 for the third consecutive day, the Colombo Stock Exchange data showed.",
        "The main All Share Price Index down 1.11% or 79.99 to 7,158.60 at 1130 hours.",
        "Most liquid index S&P SL20 down 1.15% or 26.35 points to 2,266.89.",
        "Top losers \u2013 LOLC, Sampath Bank and Lanka IOC. (Colombo/Jul07/2022)"
